(which just makes sure that getLeases() and getLock(...) is accessible and can be called from a RegionObserver implementation).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13430790" author="lhofhansl" created="Wed, 8 Aug 2012 01:10:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;BTW. this also came up in an internal Salesforce discussion and we need something the leases for some internal use cases.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13430792" author="lhofhansl" created="Wed, 8 Aug 2012 01:11:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Going to commit soon if nobody objects to the new API(s) exposed to CPs.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
